{"type":null,"faqId":48079,"title":"开启单手操作","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.3784722in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>开启单手操作模式，更易于驾驭大屏幕手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178120\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“单手操作”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>在“单手操作”界面，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>进入“单手屏幕”界面，点击“单手屏幕”开关。开启后，在虚拟导航栏区域左右滑动可调整屏幕界面的左右布局。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>进入“单手键盘”界面，点击“单手键盘”开关。开启后，点击屏幕侧方的箭头可调整拨号盘或通话中按键等的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置",